http://loftblog.ru/2013/05/21/avtomatizaciya-dlya-samyx-lenivyx-vmeste-s-grunt-js/

Requirements:
1) node.js
2) npm

Guide:

1) Install grunt
    'npm install -g grunt-cli'

2) Write plugins in package.json

3) Install plugins from package.json
It will create node_modules folder
    'npm install grunt --save-dev'
    'npm install'

4) Write Gruntfile.js

5) Start Grunt
    'grunt'


!!!
If you change some paths
CHECK it in 'package.json'

If you create/remove something in 'scg/src'
                                | 'scs/src'
                                | 'github/src'
                                | 'html/src',
CHECK 'Gruntfile.js'
!!!